CheckFail вџЁвџЁduplicateIndexвџ©, Rows вџЁ<"event-a:0", <"event-a:0"вџ©, "posting_index_duplicate"вџ©

emptyIdentity в†ђ Tx вџЁ"", "physical_fallback", 1, 4, вџЁP вџЁ0,":0"вџ©, P вџЁ1,":1"вџ©вџ©вџ©
CheckFail вџЁвџЁemptyIdentityвџ©, Rows вџЁ<":0", <":1"вџ©, "event_identity_missing"вџ©

